00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,840
I have to get there in time.

300
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,840
I'll give her a few more minutes.

301
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,840
Mom, it's an important match.

302
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,840
I promised to stay there.

303
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,840
Let's go.

304
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,840
And you'll be successful.

305
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,840
I'll try, Mom.

306
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,840
But you have so many rules.

307
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,840
You are my life.

308
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,840
I only have rules to avoid problems.

309
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,840
Nothing will happen to you.

310
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,840
I don't think so, Mom.

311
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,840
Let's go.

312
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,840
Okay, Alfredo.

313
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,840
Leave a note and tell her we'll be in the park.

314
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,840
I'll bring my keys.

315
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,840
Please, Mom.

316
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,840
We have to go.

317
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,840
I'm moving as fast as I can, son.

318
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,840
I'll be there in time.

319
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,840
Don't rush me, please.

320
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,840
Good.

321
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,840
Alfredo!

322
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,840
Have you forgotten something?

323
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,840
Thank you.

324
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,840
THE END

325
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,840
It was time you arrived.

326
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,840
Are you late?

327
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:17,840
Not yet, but they're about to start practicing.

328
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,840
It was my sister's fault. She didn't come home.

329
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,840
Let's go!

330
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,840
Thank you.

331
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,840
Yes!

332
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,840
Bravo!

333
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,840
Well done!

334
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,840
Alfredo, thank you.

335
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,840
That's it!

336
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,840
Very good, Alfredo.

337
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:53,840
That's how you do it.

338
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,840
I remember, guys. Come here.

339
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,840
Your positions are on the list.

340
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,840
Check them out and get ready to take them

341
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,840
as soon as the other team leaves, okay?

342
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,840
Are you at the bank?

343
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,840
You too.

344
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,840
I'm always there.

345
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,840
Hey, where are you going now?

346
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,840
Let's see what's going on.

347
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,840
Sir.

348
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,840
Yes?

349
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,840
I'm not playing today.

350
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,840
Well, today you'll play as an entry.

351
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,840
Why?

352
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,840
You know the rules.

353
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,840
If you don't practice, you don't play.

354
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,840
You can't do it.

355
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,840
Oh, no!

356
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,840
They're the rules.

357
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:39,840
You'll only play as an entry in the right garden.

358
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:40,840
Understood?

359
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,840
But I'm a very good player.

360
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,840
This game is important.

361
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,840
It's true.

362
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,840
I need you to play.

363
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,840
But there are many guys who have come

364
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,840
every day in time.

365
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,840
And they get really angry.

366
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:51,840
It wouldn't be fair for them not to let them play.

367
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,840
But they want you to play.

368
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,840
And if we lose?

369
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,840
If we lose, we lose.

370
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,840
When one does wrong things,

371
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,840
it hurts everyone.

372
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,840
It's not fair.

373
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,840
Well, I'll tell you something.

374
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,840
It'll be better if you get used to it, Alfredo,

375
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,840
because you'll have to respect

376
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,840
all your life rules.

377
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,840
Now let's go to the attack.

378
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,840
Go sit down.

379
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,840
Okay.

380
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,840
Cheer your team up from the bench.

381
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,840
Let's go.

382
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,840
Are you going to play?

383
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,840
Just one entry.

384
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,840
We'll lose.

385
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,840
I'm sorry.

386
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,840
I broke the rules.

387
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,840
That's terrible.

388
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,840
They won't lose.

389
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,840
I'm looking for Mrs. Silvia Martinez.

390
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:24,840
Silvia Martinez?

391
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,840
Yes, I'm Silvia Martinez.

392
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,840
I'm sorry to alarm her.

393
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,840
Can you come with me?

394
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:30,840
What happened?

395
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,840
It's her daughter.

396
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,840
Teresa, what did she do?

397
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,840
Where is she?

398
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,840
Mom, I'm sorry.

399
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,840
Teresa, what happened?

400
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,840
Eduard.

401
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,840
Eduard, what were you doing with Eduard?

402
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:43,840
Listen to me, Mom.

403
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,840
They hurt him.

404
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,840
The man who was with her daughter sold drugs.

405
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,840
Drugs?

406
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:48,840
Is Eduard dead?

407
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,840
No, but his car was destroyed.

408
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,840
He has a drug problem.

409
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,840
I didn't know anything about drugs, Mom.

410
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:55,840
I swear.

411
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,840
We believe your daughter is telling the truth, Mrs. Martinez.

412
00:12:57,840 --> 00:13:00,840
We've been watching that young man for a long time.

413
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,840
You'll work for me.

414
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,840
Can you start tomorrow?

415
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,840
Of course.

416
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,840
After my game.

417
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,840
Okay, everything is fixed.

418
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,840
Eduard gave me a job.

419
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,840
Doing what?

420
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:11,840
Sending packages.

421
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,840
What kind of packages?

422
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,840
I don't know.

423
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,840
He didn't tell me.

424
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,840
But they want me to play.

425
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:17,840
What if we lose?

426
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,840
What if we lose?

427
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,840
We lose.

428
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,840
When you do bad things,

429
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,840
you hurt others.

430
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,840
I don't understand why you don't listen to me.

431
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:24,840
I try.

432
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,840
But you have so many rules.

433
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,840
You are my life.

434
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:30,840
I have rules to avoid problems.

435
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,840
Why do you worry so much about me?

436
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:33,840
You are my friend.

437
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,840
And I don't want you to get into trouble.

438
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,840
Alfredo.

439
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:39,840
Alfredo.

440
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,840
Alfredo.

441
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:41,840
Yes, Mom.

442
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,840
Stay with Sonia until we come back, okay?

443
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:45,840
Okay.

444
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:47,840
No matter what happens, Mom.

445
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:49,840
Yes, it's true.

446
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,840
Only for me.

447
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,840
To be continued...

